<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>🌟 Divine DNA | 신성한 코드</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background: radial-gradient(80% 80% at 50% 40%, #3b1a7d 0%, #1b0e40 100%);
      font-family: "Noto Sans KR", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: #f3e8ff;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 340px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255,215,0,0.4);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.45));
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-top: 1.4rem;
      color: #ffd972;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    h2 {
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #d8c6ff;
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- 로고 이미지 -->
  <img src="./divine-dna-logo.png" alt="Divine DNA Logo" class="logo">
  <h1>신성한 DNA</h1>
  <h2>당신의 빛을 깨우세요</h2>

  <footer>© Divine DNA • 리뎀션 네트워크</footer>
</body>
</html>
